node.text: What’s up everybody, I’ve accepted the #ALLINCHALLENGE. Go to allinchallenge.com/magic-johnson to participate in the auction to play a game of HORSE ahead of sitting courtside with me at a Lakers game. Let's come together & help feed the hungry during this difficult time. @isiahthomas @samuelljackson @jimmykimmel @anthonyanderson @iamsteveharveytv @cedtheentertainer @christucker @chrisrock @officialspikelee I challenge you to be ALL IN!!

node.text: I thank you honey for guiding me back to the church, strengthening my love for the Lord, and finding us an amazing pastor, Bishop Blake, at our church home West Angeles COGIC. You are my everything, I love you!! Thank you for 30 years and I look forward to 30 more!

node.text: Cookie, our 30 year marriage has been the best time of my life. Ever since the day I laid eyes on you in 1978 I knew you were the one for me. I thank God every day for you and for bringing you into my life! You’ve made me a better man, person, husband, father, and businessman.

node.text: Cookie and I enjoyed being back at West Angeles this morning! Bishop Blake was on 🔥🔥🔥 with today’s message “The Battle is not yours but God’s” and today’s reading was from 1 Chronicles 20:15-25.

May be an image of text that says 'HYPEBEAST STORE Burberry Readies the Debut of ts Much-Anticipated Blankos Block Party' NFT Collection Set to launch later this month. 1of3 Gaming Burberry/MythicalGames 15 Hrs ago 5.3K 3 Burberry (LSE:BRBY.L +1.36%) 's long- awaited non-fungible token (NFT) collection alongside Mythical Games' Blankos Block Party is finally set to release on August 11.'.
